ew Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ушбу аризага қуйидагилар илова қилинмоқда:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 46px;\"></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 28.321329639889px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 292.12188365651px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Ҳужжатнинг реквизитлари </span></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 311.0027700831px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;\">Нусхалари сони </span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 28.321329639889px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 292.12188365651px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 1=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 311.0027700831px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 28.321329639889px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 292.12188365651px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 2=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 311.0027700831px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; margin-bottom: 0pt; text-indent: 28.333333333333px;\"></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td 3=\"\" style=\"border: 1px solid #000; width: 28.3213